import pyautogui
import time

try:
    # Press Win key to open Start menu
    pyautogui.press('win')
    time.sleep(1)
    # Type 'calculator' to search for Calculator
    pyautogui.typewrite('calculator')
    time.sleep(1)
    # Press Enter to launch Calculator
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(2)
    print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
except Exception as e:
    print("FAILED: " + str(e))
